Privacy Policy
Four Seasons uses Firebase to collect analytics data to help me make better development decisions for the app.
For non-subscribers Four Seasons may display advertisements managed by Google’s AdMob system.
Four Seasons will request Hong Kong weather data from DATA.GOV.HK and request world cities weather data from WMO World Weather Information Service. Please refer to the privacy policy of DATA.GOV.HK and WMO World Weather Information Service.
〈春夏秋冬〉使用Firebase收集分析數據，用於對app的開發做出更好的決定。
〈春夏秋冬〉可能會向非訂閲用户顯示來自Google AdMob的廣告。
〈春夏秋冬〉會向〈資料一線通〉請求香港天氣數據，向〈世界天氣信息服務網〉請求世界城市天氣數據。請參閱〈資料一線通〉和〈世界天氣信息服務網〉的私隱政策。
Terms of Use
By using Four Seasons app, you agree to be bound by this Terms of Use and by our Privacy Policy.
The weather data come from DATA.GOV.HK, and the intellectual property rights are owned by the Government of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region. Four Seasons do not response for the accuracy of the data of any third party.
使用〈春夏秋冬〉app代表你同意以下條款和我們的私隱政策。
〈春夏秋冬〉的香港天氣數據來自〈資料一線通〉，知識產權爲香港特別行政區政府擁有。〈春夏秋冬〉對所有第三方數據的準確性概不負責。